        <abstract> 
<p>Responds to CD’s query on <hi rend="italic">Subularia</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Limosella</hi>. There are discrepancies among authorities on whether <hi rend="italic">Subularia</hi> flowers out of water. <hi rend="italic">Limosella</hi> certainly flowers out of water.</p> 
